<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.1.4">
<l>puḷvāy piḷanta puṉitāveṉṟa ḻaikka</l>
<l>vuḷḷē niṉṟeṉ ṉuḷḷaṅkuḷiru moruvā</l>
<l>kaḷvā kaṭaṉmal laikkiṭantaka rumpē</l>
<l>vaḷḷā luṉṉaiyeṅ ṅaṉamnāṉmaṟak kēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Unique one who sooths my heart, remaining in [it],</l>
<l>When [I] cry out, “Pure one who split the bird’s mouth,”</l>
<l>Rogue, sugarcane who lies in Kaṭalmallai,</l>
<l>Liberal one, how [would] I forget you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
